 
<p>

A UK union representing gig workers calls for a <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2022/jul/17/union-calls-on-uk-uber-users-to-join-24-hour-strike-uber-files">one-day boycott of
Uber</a>.
<p>
If only Uber's injustice against workers concerns you, that is a
natural response.  But if Uber's injustice against customers concerns
you too, I suggest going on a permanent boycott, <a href="/uber.html">as I have</a>.

 